Exscript
--------
* Improve support for mapping hosts to specific accounts:
    Exscript.Queue.add_account(myaccount, match = lambda host: host.get_name().startswith('foo'))
* Add tests for Transport class debug levels.
* Add API docs for Exscript.parselib.
* Add a test for Exscript.Task.
* Test the exscript executable.
* Test Queue constructor kwargs.
* Create more stdlib tests like tests/templates/stdlib.crypt/.

exscriptd
---------
* Add support for this:
      <queue name="default-queue">
         ...
         <account-pool for="hostname == 'myhost'">foobar</account-pool>
      </queue>
* Make daemons asynchronous.
* Debug memory usage.
* Add more tests.
